    "Condition : 1 - The development shall be carried out in accordance with the reports, specifications and drawings detailed Signage proposal dated 18th September 2024 and site location plan dated 11th July 2024.\r\nReason: To ensure a satisfactory standard of development and to allow the local planning authority to review any potential changes to the scheme. \r\n",
